    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Erythematous, macular and/or papular\nrash\nwith well demarcated borders\nMore severe disease will also have skin maceration and erosions\nCandidal rash\nwill include scaling around margins\nClassic finding is \"satellite lesions\" in other locations\nAlso examine for\noral thrush",
